Power BI Project: Sales Performance Analytics Dashboard 
Project Overview :
This self-developed Power BI project focuses on building an end-to-end Sales Analytics Dashboard, highlighting key KPIs such as Sales, Profit %, LBS %, and Target Attainment.
The goal was to transform raw sales data into actionable business insights through efficient data modeling, DAX measures, and interactive visualization design.
________________________________________
 Key Objectives :
•	Design a clean, optimized star schema data model for sales reporting.
•	Define and calculate business KPIs and measures to support executive-level decision-making.
•	Build an interactive, user-friendly Power BI dashboard for real-time performance analysis.
________________________________________
Technical Implementation :
Data Modeling & Preparation
•	Created a star schema model integrating fact and dimension tables for better query performance.
•	Structured data relationships and ensured model integrity for accurate cross-filtering.
•	Established a dedicated Measure Table for better management of DAX calculations.
DAX & Analytics
•	Developed DAX measures for Total Sales, Profit %, Target Achievement, and LBS %.
•	Applied Time Intelligence functions to calculate Month-over-Month (MoM) and Year-to-Date (YTD) metrics.
•	Fixed context-related DAX issues ensuring correct aggregations and KPI consistency.
Visual Design & Interactivity
•	Designed dynamic trend charts using Field Parameters for easy switching between metrics.
•	Utilized the new Card visual with reference labels for modern KPI representation.
•	Created Gauge charts to visualize Profit and LBS % targets.
•	Used Group feature for building histograms and Zoom Slider for time-based analysis.
•	Applied Conditional Formatting to highlight performance thresholds within tables.
•	Designed a slicer panel for better user control and filtering experience.
Advanced Features
•	Implemented Bookmarks for navigation and interactive storytelling.
•	Fixed bookmark issues to ensure data and filter preservation.
•	Added tooltips for country-level insights and contextual drilldowns.
•	Published the report to Power BI Service for sharing and stakeholder access.
•	Hosted the project on GitHub portfolio page for professional showcasing.
________________________________________
 Outcome
•	Delivered a visually rich dashboard that enables real-time sales and profit monitoring.
•	Simplified management decision-making with interactive KPIs and trend visuals.
•	Demonstrated expertise in data modeling, DAX, visualization design, and user experience.
________________________________________
Tools & Technologies
Power BI | DAX | Power Query | SQL | Star Schema | GitHub
